Customer Realtionship Manager helps to:

Use of HTML, CSS, JSP, Hibrnate 5 and Spring MVC technologies.

Functionalities-

1. Add a new customer using Hiberate with the help of Add button.
2. Update an existing customer
3. Delete an existing customer
4. List all the customers present
5. Sort the customers based on First name, last name or email. By default - Last name sorting
7. Searching of customers
  a) If search customer field is blank- Search all the customers
